SQL_STMT_U.val: Select P01.EF_TYP,P01.FST_NO from PRD004 P04, PRD001 P01 where P04.PLN_CD = ':1' and P04.PLN_DAT >= ':2' and P04.PLN_DAT < ':3' and P04.IND_CHA_TYP = ' ' and P04.IND_CHA_NO = 0 and P01.MTOCD = P04.MTOCD group by P01.EF_TYP,P01.FST_NO
Select P01.EF_TYP,P01.FST_NO from PRD020 P20, PRD001 P01 where P20.PLN_CD = ':1' and P20.PLN_DAT >= ':2' and P20.PLN_DAT < ':3' and P01.MTOCD = P20.MTOCD group by P01.EF_TYP,P01.FST_NO

Select P20.PLN_CD, P20.PLN_MY, P20.PLN_DAT, P20.PLN_RES, P20.MTOCD, P20.COL_CD, P20.COLI_CD, P01.MTONAM, P01.EFM, P01.CTEGRY from PRD020 P20, PRD001 P01 where P20.PLN_CD = ':1' and P20.PLN_MY >= ':2' and P20.PLN_MY <= ':3' and P20.MTOCD = P01.MTOCD (+) order by P20.MTOCD, P20.COL_CD, P20.COLI_CD, P20.PLN_DAT
